title: Mae Ra Jiveh - Vegetarian Food Shop
description: Wholesale and retail sales of all kinds of vegan food. Has a broad range of dried, canned and frozen mock meats and vegetable proteins, seasonings, and more. The shop is hard to find, not always open and doesn't have a real shop front. Recommended to call first and to bring along somebody who speaks Khmer.
streetAddress: No 7B, Street 284, Sangkat Olympic, Khan Chamkarmon
